self.input_image_shape = K.placeholder(shape=(2,))
output = self.model.output
output.sort(key=lambda x: int(x.shape[1]))
boxes, scores, classes = yolo_eval(output, self.anchors, len(self.
    class_names), self.input_image_shape, score_threshold=self.
    score_threshold, iou_threshold=self.iou_threshold)
return boxes, scores, classes
